{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":100,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_ji_yan_ran","speaker_name":"纪嫣然","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"柔姊是个非常坚强和勇敢的女子，嫣然自问没有她的勇气。","tone":"无奈","chapter":112,"line_start":6,"line_end":8},{"speaker":"char_teng_yi","speaker_name":"滕翼","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"希望她一路平安，有一天到咸阳来找我们吧！","tone":"欣慰","chapter":112,"line_start":10,"line_end":12},{"speaker":"char_jing_jun","speaker_name":"荆俊","listener":"char_teng_yi","text":"三哥去追她回来好吗？求求她说不定她会回心转意。","tone":"恳求","chapter":112,"line_start":14,"line_end":16},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_jing_jun","text":"每一个人也应有权去追求自己的理想，选择欢喜的生活方式，否则哪有痛快可言。","tone":"平静","chapter":112,"line_start":18,"line_end":20},{"speaker":"char_lv_bu_wei","speaker_name":"吕不韦","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"今趟少龙最厉害处，是没有让人识破真正身份，此事对出征东周大大有利，趁现在六国乱成一团，正是用兵的最佳时机。","tone":"陈述","chapter":112,"line_start":42,"line_end":44},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_lv_bu_wei","text":"原来吕相已做好灭周的部署，嘿！为何不见我的丈人呢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":112,"line_start":46,"line_end":48},{"speaker":"char_lv_bu_wei","speaker_name":"吕不韦","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"少龙的归来，乃属高度机密，赵穆的事更不能宣扬出去，就当来的只是邹先生和纪才女好了，否则必让六国的奸细猜到少龙和他们的关系。只有把六国蒙在鼓里，我们才能以迅雷不及掩耳的手法，借口东周君对我大秦图谋不轨，把他拔除。","tone":"严肃","chapter":112,"line_start":50,"line_end":54},{"speaker":"char_lv_bu_wei","speaker_name":"吕不韦","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"灭周在军事上只是小事一件，却牵连甚广，一个不好，可能惹来六国联手来攻之祸。所以我们须在军事、外交两方面双管齐下，才可安享战胜的成果。","tone":"严肃","chapter":112,"line_start":60,"line_end":64},{"speaker":"char_lv_bu_wei","speaker_name":"吕不韦","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"以阳泉君为首的一群秦人，四出散播谣言，诬指本相毒害先王，又说太子乃我和王后所出，现正密谋改立大王次子成蟜。哼！我要教他们死无葬身之地，妻妾女儿全体沦为供人蹂躏的歌姬娼妓，始可泄得我心头这口恶气。","tone":"冷酷","chapter":112,"line_start":68,"line_end":72},{"speaker":"char_lv_bu_wei","speaker_name":"吕不韦","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"幸好大王对我鼎力支持，又有王后在他面前说项，现在你更擒得赵穆回来，待我灭掉东周后，便一举把阳泉君等除掉，那时大秦还有谁敢不看我吕不韦的脸色行事。","tone":"得意","chapter":112,"line_start":78,"line_end":80},{"speaker":"char_lv_bu_wei","speaker_name":"吕不韦","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"旅途辛苦，少龙好好到牧场休息，养足精神后，我还有极为重要的任务要你去办。","tone":"陈述","chapter":112,"line_start":86,"line_end":88}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_shan_rou","name":"善柔","alias":[],"identity":"赵国女刺客","faction":null,"role":"npc","archetype":"assassin","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"独来独往的女刺客，与项少龙有旧情，离别后孤身远去","personality":{"traits":["坚强","勇敢","独立","果断","孤傲"],"speech_style":"简练有力","temperament":"外冷内热"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_xiang_shao_long","type":"恋人","intensity":60,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"离别"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[112],"source_refs":[{"chapter":112,"line_start":4,"line_end":8,"text":"项少龙目送善柔的孤身单骑，逐渐消失在苍茫草野中"}]},{"id":"char_ji_yan_ran","name":"纪嫣然","alias":["纪才女"],"identity":"才女","faction":null,"role":"companion","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"天下闻名的才女，文武双全，项少龙的妻子之一","personality":{"traits":["聪慧","温柔","大方","善解人意","坚强"],"speech_style":"温柔典雅","temperament":"温柔"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_xiang_shao_long","type":"恋人","intensity":90,"bond_level":5,"dynamic":"夫妻"},{"target":"char_zou_yan","type":"亲属","intensity":70,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"义父女"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[112],"source_refs":[{"chapter":112,"line_start":6,"line_end":8,"text":"纪嫣然轻叹道"}]},{"id":"char_teng_yi","name":"滕翼","alias":["滕二哥"],"identity":"项少龙二哥","faction":null,"role":"companion","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"项少龙的二哥，精兵团成员，武艺高强","personality":{"traits":["沉稳","忠诚","豪爽","勇猛","重情义"],"speech_style":"沉稳有力","temperament":"沉稳"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_xiang_shao_long","type":"挚友","intensity":95,"bond_level":5,"dynamic":"结义兄弟"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[112],"source_refs":[{"chapter":112,"line_start":10,"line_end":12,"text":"右方的滕翼点头同意"}]},{"id":"char_jing_jun","name":"荆俊","alias":["小俊"],"identity":"项少龙四弟","faction":null,"role":"com